translate portuguese adrians1_5ca95384:

    # gg "Well, I grew up in Whiterock, but my mom and I moved here two years ago so that I could go to school at Skyhill."
    gg "Bem, eu cresci em Whiterock, mas a minha mãe e eu mudámo-nos para cá há dois anos para que eu pudesse estudar em Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:16
translate portuguese adrians1_cd22b14e:

    # pc "Don't they have a pretty good school in Whiterock?"
    pc "Não têm uma escola bastante boa em Whiterock?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:17
translate portuguese adrians1_ee7879cc:

    # gg "Yeah they do."
    gg "Sim, têm."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:18
translate portuguese adrians1_e8ea576e:

    # gg "But we both wanted to get away from there and kind of start over."
    gg "Mas nós as duas queríamos afastar-nos de lá e, de certa forma, recomeçar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:19
translate portuguese adrians1_3a43b4ac:

    # pc "I understand that. I did that a few years ago too."
    pc "Eu entendo isso. Eu também fiz isso há alguns anos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:21
translate portuguese adrians1_f9de9be2:

    # gg "Oh yeah?"
    gg "Ah, é?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:22
translate portuguese adrians1_208373f4:

    # pc "Yeah, I left Skyhill and moved to Brazil for three years."
    pc "Sim, deixei Skyhill e mudei-me para o Brasil por três anos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:23
translate portuguese adrians1_515d9d9f:

    # gg "Wow! Brazil?"
    gg "Uau! Brasil?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:24
translate portuguese adrians1_5682a613:

    # pc "For school."
    pc "Para estudar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:25
translate portuguese adrians1_2618bc65:

    # gg "They have good schools in Brazil?"
    gg "Tem boas escolas no Brasil?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:26
translate portuguese adrians1_0018c80a:

    # pc "For quantum physics, yeah."
    pc "Para física quântica, sim."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:27
translate portuguese adrians1_0e5ea782:

    # pc "I mostly just needed to get away for a while though."
    pc "Mas, na verdade, eu só precisava de me afastar por um tempo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:29
translate portuguese adrians1_1cbefdb2:

    # gg "Yeah, we just needed new lives. I left everything behind and became a new Adrian."
    gg "Sim, só precisávamos de novas vidas. Deixei tudo para trás e tornei-me um novo Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:30
translate portuguese adrians1_6be34fc8:

    # gg "That's why I don't have a bunch of friends though. I didn't really stay in contact with anybody from Whiterock."
    gg "É por isso que não tenho muitos amigos. Não mantive contacto com ninguém de Whiterock."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:31
translate portuguese adrians1_3b69fa7a:

    # pc "Well I'm your friend if you ever need to talk about anything."
    pc "Bem, sou teu amigo se precisares de falar sobre alguma coisa."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:32
translate portuguese adrians1_3e729810:

    # gg "Thanks, [pcname]. I'll probably take you up on that some time."
    gg "Obrigado, [pcname]. Provavelmente vou aproveitar essa oferta um dia destes."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:34
translate portuguese adrians1_083372d1:

    # gg "I'm really glad we sat next to each other in Social Studies."
    gg "Estou muito contente por nos termos sentado lado a lado na aula de Estudos Sociais."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians1.rpy:35
translate portuguese adrians1_03eaad50:

    # pc "Me too."
    pc "Eu também."

